{"about_the_game":"Xeroes is a fast-paced brawl-action game featuring charming characters and innovative combat mechanics. Whether you're teaming up with friends or embarking on solo adventures, Xeroes offers a diverse array of game modes that cater to every playstyle, each designed to enhance your gaming experience. Dive into the action and enjoy the exciting world of Xeroes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Original and Unique Characters Design</strong></li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998940/extras/1.gif?t=1737003878\" /><br>Characters that are uniquely designed based on their theme, are coming to life! Master their abilities, bringing your favourite Xero to battle! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Level Design Based on Real World Myth &amp; Legends</strong></li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998940/extras/2.gif?t=1737003878\" /><br>Designed to be familiar and immersive, all levels are created for the sole purpose - excitement! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Character Customization with Fun and Unique Skins</strong></li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998940/extras/3.gif?t=1737003878\" /><br>From skins, companions to each detailed cosmetics, power fragments are free for you to customise at your will! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Different play styles to suit different players</strong></li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998940/extras/4.gif?t=1737003878\" /><br>Diversity of classes and multiple playstyles of character to choose, you won\u2019t fall for only 1 Xero forever! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Multiple game modes</strong></li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamsta